================================================================================
MODIFICATIONS
================================================================================

The following files have been modified from the original GPUStack project:

Modified files:
  - gpustack/schemas/model_provider.py
      Added: customBaseUrlAnthropic, auth_style_anthropic, strip_fields fields
             to CustomProviderConfig; dual base URL support via get_base_url(fmt)

  - gpustack/routes/model_provider.py
      Added: build_openai_url() for versioned API path handling (get-models + test-model)
             Custom auth_style support via AuthAdapter (get-models + test-model)
             _parse_model_list() for robust multi-format response parsing

  - gpustack/routes/model_routes.py
      Added: supported_formats filling from provider config in target queries

  - gpustack/schemas/model_routes.py
      Added: supported_formats field to ModelRouteTargetPublic

  - gpustack/routes/openai.py
      Modified: integrated FormatRouter for provider proxy with format conversion

  - gpustack/gateway/ai_proxy_types.py
      Added: customBaseUrlAnthropic, authStyleAnthropic, supportedFormats,
             authStyle, stripFields fields to CustomConfig

New files:
  - gpustack/converter/ (new module)
      converters.py  — Anthropic <-> OpenAI request/response conversion
      streaming.py   — SSE streaming format conversion
      router.py      — Format routing (passthrough vs convert)
      auth.py        — Auth adapter (Bearer / X-API-Key / Auto)
      urls.py        — URL building with versioned path handling
      provider_proxy.py — Unified provider proxy with retry and format conversion

  - tests/test_converter.py
      Unit tests for the converter module (55 tests)

  - gpustack-ui/src/pages/maas-provider/hooks/use-provider-required-fields.tsx
      Added: supported_formats, customBaseUrlAnthropic, auth_style_anthropic,
             strip_fields field definitions for Custom provider

  - gpustack-ui/src/pages/maas-provider/forms/provider-configs.tsx
      Added: Checkbox rendering, conditional visibility via dependsOn,
             Form.useWatch for reactive form updates

  - gpustack-ui/src/locales/zh-CN/provider.ts
  - gpustack-ui/src/locales/en-US/provider.ts
      Added: i18n labels for new configuration fields
